if you have a long illness,

314
00:14:43,310 --> 00:14:44,870
I can really treat you.

315
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,650
Don't be ungrateful.

316
00:14:46,950 --> 00:14:48,430
Who wants to stay at your inn?

317
00:14:48,430 --> 00:14:49,520
You old fraud.

318
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:50,830
I made this rule

319
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:52,260
