326
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:09,150
Then I'll tell

327
00:15:09,150 --> 00:15:10,750
the history of this place.

328
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,220
During the Six Dynasties period,

329
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:14,710
the great monk Master Moshi

330
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:16,670
built a temple

331
00:15:16,990 --> 00:15:18,620
between Hanzhou and Chang'an.

332
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:22,150
During construction, he was threatened by the thieves who dug for gold and silver.

333
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:23,430
Master was unmoved

334
00:15:23,450 --> 00:15:24,540
and remained focused.

335
00:15:24,540 --> 00:15:26,740
Not only did he built the Vajra Temple,

336
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,790
he also translated many scriptures

337
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:31,190
that have been handed down from generation to generation.

338
00:15:31,190 --> 00:15:32,120
And eventually,

339
00:15:32,230 --> 00:15:34,080
he reformed those robbers.

340
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:35,920
I think this should be

341
00:15:36,140 --> 00:15:37,740
the site of the Vajra Temple.

342
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:41,420
You're just guessing, aren't you?

343
00:15:41,420 --> 00:15:43,170
No, I'm not.

344
00:15:43,790 --> 00:15:44,990
In this season,

345
00:15:45,510 --> 00:15:46,870
there still are green onions and chives

346
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:48,860
growing on the hillside outside.

347
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:49,970
In the heavy snow,

348
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:52,660
they still remain lush and green.

349
00:15:52,690 --> 00:15:54,200
It can be said to be a marvel.

350
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:57,600
It's a sign that there're gold and silver under the mountain.

351
00:15:57,670 --> 00:16:00,870
Just as the saying goes, if there're green onions on the mountain, there's silver under it;

352
00:16:00,870 --> 00:16:03,860
If there're chives on the mountain, there's gold under it.

353
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:05,950
Moreover, in the ancient book

354
00:16:05,980 --> 00:16:07,870
"Record of the Six Dynasties Lost Works" from the Sui Dynasty,

355
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:09,150
it was recorded

356
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:11,540
that there were green onions and chives

357
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:13,400
growing around the Vajra Temple.

358
00:16:13,990 --> 00:16:15,350
I also saw a stone lantern

359
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:16,480
of the Six Dynasties

360
00:16:16,740 --> 00:16:18,960
on the hillside a few miles away.

361
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,950
Although the inscription is blurred,

362
00:16:22,350 --> 00:16:23,710
I think

363
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:28,350
the words should be "Turn a Robber into a Buddha."

364
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,930
Also,

365
00:16:29,990 --> 00:16:31,390
this place is located

366
00:16:31,430 --> 00:16:33,020
right between Hanzhou and Chang'an.

367
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:34,050
Everything fits.

368
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:35,680
Therefore, I deduce

369
00:16:35,950 --> 00:16:36,900
that this is

370
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:38,750
the site of the Vajra Temple.

371
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:42,100
What I said

372
00:16:42,730 --> 00:16:43,850
is unique skills.

373
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:46,150
You only talked.

374
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,470
What?

375
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:50,040
Doesn't this count?

376
00:16:52,110 --> 00:16:53,740
But if I don't let you in,

377
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:56,830
you'll definitely say I don't keep my word.

378
00:16:57,430 --> 00:16:58,100
Fine.

379
00:16:58,680 --> 00:16:59,670
Then I'll cut you some slack

380
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:00,690
and let you in.

381
00:17:01,070 --> 00:17:02,210
But he

382
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:04,190
can only stay at the woodshed.

383
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:05,119
Why?

384
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:08,040
Because you ate the chicken and didn't pay for it.

385
00:17:08,780 --> 00:17:09,510
Lu Lingfeng.

386
00:17:09,990 --> 00:17:11,310
She's disrespectful

387
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:12,390
to your savior.

388
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:13,790
Drink more alcohol.

389
00:17:13,990 --> 00:17:14,990
Once you're warm,

390
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:16,150
