391
00:17:16,150 --> 00:17:17,550
staying at the woodshed.

392
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:19,010
Lu Lingfeng.

393
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,650
Which side are you on?

394
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:23,650
I think Lu Lingfeng is right.

395
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:25,300
If you stay at the woodshed alone,

396
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:26,740
you can drink as much as you want.

397
00:17:26,740 --> 00:17:27,880
No one will say you drink too much.

398
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:28,880
Isn't that great?

399
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:29,830
I'm not staying at the woodshed.

400
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:31,760
I want to stay at the superior room.

401
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:03,630
One scholar.

402
00:18:04,990 --> 00:18:05,850
Two merchants.

403
00:18:05,950 --> 00:18:07,590
One of them is Sogdian.

404
00:18:08,150 --> 00:18:09,920
He does either spice business

405
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:11,310
or jewelry business.

406
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:14,150
As for the other one...

407
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:18,910
He's either a hero

408
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:21,020
or an assassin.

409
00:18:22,550 --> 00:18:23,510
Stop looking.

410
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:26,390
They're all here to take shelter from the heavy snow.

411
00:18:26,390 --> 00:18:27,030
Follow me.

412
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:35,110
How is it?

413
00:18:35,450 --> 00:18:36,990
The superior room is nice, isn't it?

414
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:38,320
I have to tell you first.

415
00:18:38,330 --> 00:18:39,260
It's not cheap.

416
00:18:40,710 --> 00:18:42,520
It's understandable that it's a bit expensive.

417
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:44,270
After all, the heavy snow blocked the mountain.

418
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:46,110
We're in the middle of nowhere.

419
00:18:46,130 --> 00:18:48,270
500 coins per person for each of the four of you.

420
00:18:48,270 --> 00:18:49,990
150 coins for the one staying at the woodshed.

421
00:18:49,990 --> 00:18:51,390
500 coins for the four horses.

422
00:18:51,390 --> 00:18:53,060
1,000 coins for your food and drink.

423
00:18:53,060 --> 00:18:54,640
The total is

424
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:56,350
3,650 coins.

425
00:18:57,670 --> 00:18:58,220
This...

426
00:18:59,430 --> 00:19:00,230
So expensive?

427
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:01,470
That's the price.

428
00:19:01,470 --> 00:19:03,330
If you're not staying, leave now.

429
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:05,050
Mr. Lu.

430
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,990
We can't be taken advantage of

431
00:19:06,990 --> 00:19:07,580
and be tricked.

432
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:08,110
Let's go.

433
00:19:08,150 --> 00:19:08,910
Let's go.

434
00:19:08,950 --> 00:19:10,160
Let's go.

435
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:10,950
Wait.

436
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:16,430
Xijun.

437
00:19:17,260 --> 00:19:18,990
She's charging an unreasonable price.

438
00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:20,050
We're not staying.

439
00:19:24,290 --> 00:19:24,900
Landlady.

440
00:19:25,180 --> 00:19:26,720
Your price is too high.

441
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,630
If it weren't for the strong winds and heavy snow,

442
00:19:28,630 --> 00:19:30,890
