445
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:36,190
But we want two superior rooms.

446
00:19:36,190 --> 00:19:37,270
The food must be good.

447
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:39,000
And the alcohol must be enough.

448
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:43,670
Okay.

449
00:19:44,430 --> 00:19:46,510
The superior room next door is also for you.

450
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,500
How to arrange rooms

451
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:48,470
is up to you.

452
00:19:51,910 --> 00:19:52,510
But he

453
00:19:52,900 --> 00:19:54,360
must stay at the woodshed.

454
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:00,670
You...

455
00:20:07,870 --> 00:20:09,710
You know that this is a clip joint.

456
00:20:09,710 --> 00:20:11,270
Why do you insist on staying here?

457
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:12,000
Lu Lingfeng.

458
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:14,150
He's doing it for fun.

459
00:20:14,150 --> 00:20:15,680
What are you doing this for?

460
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:18,230
You've been delayed in Shiyang

461
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:19,490
for more than ten days.

462
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:20,790
Aren't you in a hurry to take office

463
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:21,550
in Yunding?

464
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:25,140
And you, Xijun.

465
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,160
Five people and four horses.

466
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:28,630
She charged too much money.

467
00:20:28,630 --> 00:20:29,630
You just paid her?

468
00:20:29,840 --> 00:20:31,370
It's indeed too expensive.

469
00:20:34,890 --> 00:20:35,620
Chicken Fed.

