475
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:48,750
Xijun, you also learnt smokescreens.

476
00:20:49,770 --> 00:20:51,190
What you did just now was to avoid

477
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:52,520
arousing the suspicion

478
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:53,870
of that landlady?

479
00:20:54,150 --> 00:20:54,680
Exactly.

480
00:20:59,530 --> 00:21:00,990
If this is really a clip joint,

481
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:02,350
those people downstairs

482
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:04,010
should all be on the same side.

483
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:06,750
Otherwise, with just the landlady

484
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,880
and that old waiter,

485
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,150
she wouldn't have dared to let us

486
00:21:09,150 --> 00:21:10,280
stay here together.

487
00:21:11,630 --> 00:21:13,820
-That old waiter...
-That old waiter...

488
00:21:13,820 --> 00:21:14,670
You go first.

489
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:16,160
Just now, I intentionally

490
00:21:16,390 --> 00:21:18,450
