491
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:19,920
It's a little heavy.

492
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:21,200
It's just a stick.

493
00:21:21,870 --> 00:21:23,670
But when he used it...

494
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:27,350
I once patrolled the frontier with my master.

495
00:21:27,990 --> 00:21:30,150
The posture he used when he moved

496
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:33,550
looks quite familiar.

497
00:21:40,690 --> 00:21:42,220
What are you talking about?

498
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:47,750
Wait.

499
00:21:59,030 --> 00:21:59,990
Nothing's wrong.

500
00:21:59,990 --> 00:22:01,120
You can drink it now.

501
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,740
