505
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:10,870
If something is put in the water,

506
00:22:10,870 --> 00:22:12,090
when Yong'an Pill is added,

507
00:22:12,090 --> 00:22:13,290
bubbles will appear.

508
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,040
Yingtao.

509
00:22:14,470 --> 00:22:15,670
Impressive.

510
00:22:16,470 --> 00:22:17,630
It's just a petty trick.

511
00:22:17,630 --> 00:22:20,470
Petty tricks can sometimes be of great use.

512
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:23,790
This kind of inn built in the remote area

513
00:22:24,390 --> 00:22:27,030
