514
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:28,570
and a main room in the middle.

515
00:22:28,570 --> 00:22:30,570
How come there's an ancestral hall?

516
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,790
And it's so ancient too.

517
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,460
It's not only ancient.

518
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:41,830
The construction method of this ancestral hall

519
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,990
