523
00:22:49,550 --> 00:22:50,750
It seems familiar to me,

524
00:22:50,750 --> 00:22:51,760
but I can't remember

525
00:22:51,760 --> 00:22:53,220
where I've seen it before.

526
00:22:58,830 --> 00:22:59,630
On my way here,

527
00:22:59,910 --> 00:23:01,390
