536
00:23:15,950 --> 00:23:17,080
That's why I'm fine.

537
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:22,760
Landlady.

538
00:23:24,430 --> 00:23:25,090
I'm coming.

539
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:27,830
Another one came.

540
00:23:28,590 --> 00:23:29,510
I'd like to see

541
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:31,430
what unique skill he has.

542
00:24:04,150 --> 00:24:05,750
I'm Hermit Jiang.

543
00:24:06,670 --> 00:24:07,800
It's been snowing heavily.

544
00:24:07,800 --> 00:24:09,000
I'd like to stay here.

545
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:09,830
Landlady,

546
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,570
