550
00:24:18,470 --> 00:24:19,710
I own this inn.

551
00:24:19,790 --> 00:24:21,070
The rules are made by me.

552
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:22,070
What's it to you?

553
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:25,740
If the heavy snow continues for a few more days,

554
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:27,400
the food at my inn

555
00:24:27,430 --> 00:24:28,310
may not be enough.

556
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:29,740
Then I'll have to go to the town

557
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:30,990
dozens of miles away to buy it.

558
00:24:30,990 --> 00:24:32,070
The weather is so cold.

559
00:24:32,070 --> 00:24:33,410
I don't want to bother.

560
00:24:33,630 --> 00:24:34,960
Who said that?

561
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:36,620
For this distinguished guest,

562
00:24:36,620 --> 00:24:37,870
I'm willing to bother.

563
00:24:37,870 --> 00:24:38,530
Step aside.

564
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:39,270
No!

565
00:24:40,630 --> 00:24:41,890
Hermit.

566
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:44,030
This inn isn't a place where ordinary people

567
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:44,870
can stay.

568
00:24:45,270 --> 00:24:46,750
If you want to rest here,

569
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:49,270
you must show your unique skill.

570
00:24:49,470 --> 00:24:49,950
You...

571
00:24:50,230 --> 00:24:50,890
You what?

572
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:53,960
If you want to use your good looks

573
00:24:54,150 --> 00:24:56,280
to make this landlady change the rule,

574
00:24:56,550 --> 00:24:57,920
then please go in.

575
00:24:58,430 --> 00:25:00,350
After all, it's her who owns the inn

576
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:01,660
and makes the rules.

577
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:04,040
It's inappropriate for me to say more.

578
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,390
Ignore this old drunkard

579
00:25:05,390 --> 00:25:07,050
